Determine the force in member [`CF`] of the truss shown above and indicate whether the member is in tension or compression. Assume each member is connected by a pin.


[`F_{CF}`] = [_____]{$Fcf} [`\textrm{kN}`]

[@ $mfcf->buttons() @]*  

END_PGML
